<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title> After Login</title>
	<style type="text/css">
	
body{
background:#e9e9e9;	
font-family: lucida grande,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;
}

#wrapper{

background-color:white;
margin-top:100px;
padding:10px;
border:5px solid black;

}

h1{
font-family: cooper black;
text-align:center;
}

h2{
font-family: algerian;
color:black;
text-align:center;
margin-top:10px;
}

h3{
font-family: algerian;
color:black;
margin-top:10px;
margin-left:10px;	
}
li{
font-weight:bold;
margin-left:10px;	
}

p{
font-family: arial;	
margin-top:100px;
background:none;
color: black;
border:5px solid black;

}

#wrapper{
width:1080px;
background-color:white;
margin:0 auto;
padding:10px;
border:5px solid black;

}


ul#nav,ul.sub1{
list-style-type:none;
font-size:15pt;

}
ul#nav li{

font-size:25px;
float:left;
position:relative;
text-align:center;
width:240px;
height:30px;
margin-right:4px;
}
ul#nav a:link,nav a:active, nav a:visited{ 
display:block;
color:black;
text-decoration:none;
width:240px;
height:30px;
line-height:30px;
background-color:powderblue;
border:2px solid black;
border-radius:5px;

}
ul#nav .sub1 a{

	margin-top:3px;

}
ul#nav li:hover >a{
	background-color:blue;
	
	
}
ul#nav li:hover a:hover{
	background-color:#fff;
    color:blue;

}
ul#nav .sub1{
	display:none;
    position:absolute;
    top:26px;
	left:0px;
}

ul#nav .sub1 li{	
	margin-top:5px;
	
	
}

ul#nav li:hover .sub1{
	display: block;
}
.darrow{
	font-size:15pt;
	position:absolute;
	top:3px;
	right:4px;
}
	</style>	

</head>

<body class="homepage">
    <div id="wrapper">
			<h1>WELCOME! Mr.Manager! </h1>
			<h2>You can access all the following informations as a manager!</h2>
			<nav id="navigation">
				<ul id="nav">
				<li><%= link_to "HOME", root_path %></li>
					
				<li><a href="#">EDIT INFO</a><span class="darrow">&#9660;</span>
				
					<ul class="sub1">
						<li><%= link_to "HOSTEL", hostels_path %></li>
						<li><%= link_to "MANAGER", managers_path %></li>
						<li><%= link_to "SEATS", seats_path %></li>
						<li><%= link_to "STUDENTS", students_path %></li>
						
						<li><%= link_to "PAYMENTS", payments_path %></li>
						<li><%= link_to "VISITORS", visitors_path %></li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li><%= link_to :LOGOUT, destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete  %></li>   
			</nav>

			<p>
			<h2>INSTRUCTIONS:</h2>
			<h3>VIEW DETAILS:</h3>			
			
			<li>You can see the information of all entities of this system by selecting options under VIEW DETAILS"</li>
			
			<h3>EDIT INFO:</h3>
			<li>Select table from drop-down menu of 'EDIT INFO'.</li>
			<li>Enter data of all attributes of first table to INSERT new row.</li>
			<li>Enter data only in first attribute of first table(Primary key) to DELETE any row.</li>
			<li>Enter existing data in in first table and desired data in respective attributes of the second table to UPDATE.</li>
			<li>Click on DISPLAY button to view the whole table.</li>
			<li>Enter data only in first attribute of first table(Primary key) to SEARCH info of respective row.</li>
			</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>